column1: This file is a look up table to be used for EUI/RUI for 3D organ models from Visible human female and male produced by Kristen Browne NIH/NIAID on behalf of HuBMAP MC-IU collaboration.

Models used are v1.0 uploaded for Nature Cell Biology submission
